description:
ReviewDB  

A plugin that lets you leave reviews on user's profiles like they're a product on Amazon. Any user will be able to see your review no matter what client mod or platform they are on, as long as they have a ReviewDB plugin!

Made with lots & lots of help from <@581573474296791211> <a:flowercat:1084310943296663613>
Database created & hosted by <@287555395151593473>  

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/StupidityDB/EnmityPlugin/master/dist/ReviewDB.js
Source: https://github.com/StupidityDB/EnmityPlugin
